WEBVTT

00:12:59.640 --> 00:13:02.936
You can see that Europe is on the edge.

00:13:02.960 --> 00:13:06.016
And we in Exeter today

00:13:06.040 --> 00:13:08.976
are on the far edge of the planet.

00:13:09.000 --> 00:13:11.976
We are on a tiny scrap of rock

00:13:12.000 --> 00:13:13.696
off Europe

00:13:13.720 --> 00:13:16.336
which contains less than one percent

00:13:16.360 --> 00:13:18.376
of the world's adults,

00:13:18.400 --> 00:13:20.936
and less than half a percent

00:13:20.960 --> 00:13:22.800
of the world's children.

00:13:23.640 --> 00:13:28.256
We are living in a stabilizing world,
an urbanizing world,

00:13:28.280 --> 00:13:30.256
an aging world,